postman
Get:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/user/  - get all users
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/transaction/ - get all transaction
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/type_of_service/ - get all type of service
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/get_zero_point/ - get all users with zero points
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/get_non_zero_point/ - get all users with 1000+ points


Post:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/user/ create  new user
{
    "username": "username",
    "password": "password"
}

http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/transaction/  - create transaction
{
    "author": "2",
    "type_of_service": "69"
    "status": "accrual" or "write-off"
}

http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/type_of_service/ create new type of service
{
    "name": "name",
    "point": "5"
}